<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Oct1917"><font color="red">22 October 1917</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): I came here a few days ago &hellip; I am glad <cite>Ulysses</cite> is to appear in both reviews from March on and now that I can read and write again I shall get to work. I hope you will both like it.</div>
